Got a problem with Kerbalstuff. I've been trying to publish update to my mod, but after upload progress bar reaches end, nothing happens.

This is my 3rd update for that mod, didn't have that problem with previous updates. Any idea what's going on?

Edited December 5, 2015 by GagaX

I suggest you pop into #kerbalstuff on IRC, we might be able to help you more from there. I'll take a look at your mod page, but I don't know if I'll be able to fix it myself, mightr have to come from Sircmpwn

 

EDIT: nope doesn't seem like I can do much on my side.
